{
  "stem": "10572.7",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Erwin, who had become a good buddy of mine, called me and said, my gosh.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, you almost got me court-martialed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, what happened?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, you sent that little bastard in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when he saw the black eagle on my battle jacket, he started to shake.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I knew there was something wrong.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I looked in his file, and I saw that he had killed 25 of my buddies.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I lost my temper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My Irish temper went through with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I lifted him up and threw him against the wall that he almost went through the back walls.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he had to be hospitalized.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and I said, you know, I didn't think of it one moment when I sent him to you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, he said, I'm grateful you did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he also called me one day and told me that one of the PWs had come to him and said there was a counterintelligence agent who used to be a high-ranking Hitler Youth leader.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "His name was Frank Shurman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- and Erwin called me and he said, you know-- he said, I always knew there was something wrong with you.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He said, but now I have the goods on you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I said, is he in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, yeah, he's in the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I said, I'm coming out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Went from Baltimore to Fort Meade.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he bought this guy in who had made the statement.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, you know, we're very grateful to you to tip us off about this high-ranking-- ranking Hitler Youth leader.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, can you describe him to me?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, well, I don't know him personally.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, a friend of mine told me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said well, where's the friend?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
